<div class="html_content"><p><span style="font-family:'Roboto Slab','Arial';font-weight:700;font-size:1.857em;color:rgba(53,181,235,1);">DO YOU THINK YOU BELONG HERE?</span></p><p style="margin:2.14em 0em 0.36em 0em;line-height:1.69014084507042;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto','Arial';font-size:1.143em;color:rgba(105,105,105,1);">In Africa, unemployment especially among young people remains one of the largest challenges. While entrepreneurship continue to grow at an accelerated pace, entrepreneurs still face a myriad of challenges in the marketplace in their journey to start up or scale their companies. At the same time larger organizations across a range of sectors are facing a shortage of professionals with the requisite skills to fill their workforce needs. Creativity & Innovation are the backbone of enterprise development and at Outliers By Design we equip entrepreneurs with competitive skills to help them identify innovative business ideas, create and scale new ventures and learn first-hand from industry renowned and experienced experts on best practice to grow their ventures</span></p><p style="margin:1.43em 0em 0.36em 0em;line-height:1.69014084507042;"><span><a HREF="contact.html" target="_self" class="btn btn-md btn-primary">Contact us</a></span></p></div>
